text: "Josephine" is a 1985 song by English singer Chris Rea. It is the second single from his seventh studio album Shamrock Diaries. It went to number 67 in the United Kingdom and was a top ten in France and the Netherlands. In 2000 it was sampled by French band Superfunk for their 2000 single Lucky Star. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1985 songs Category:Chris Rea songs Category:Soft rock songs
